longBusinessSummary: E79 Resources Corp., a resource exploration company, engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties. The company primarily explores for gold. It holds 100% interest in the Beaufort Project located in the southwest of Victoria, Australia; and holds interest in Myrtleford Project located in the north-east of Victoria, Australia. The company also holds a 100% interest in the Golden Girl Property located in British Columbia, Canada. E79 Resources Corp. was formerly known as Top Exploration Inc. and changed its name to E79 Resources Corp. in October 2020. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
